Episode 17

23
00:01:42,539 --> 00:01:43,859
Your Highness.

24
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:46,139
Hao Du sent a message,

25
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:49,099
saying that Princess Yongning used Li Shisi as the alias name

26
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:52,059
and assisted the governor Gongsun Heng in Shuozhou

27
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,699
to protect the city from enemies' attack.

28
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:55,338
After Shuozhou was conquered,

29
00:01:55,339 --> 00:01:57,419
Princess Yongning got caught by Ashile Tribe.

30
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:59,538
Hao Du sent someone following them.

31
00:01:59,539 --> 00:02:02,889
And the scout saw it himself, that Princess Yongning

32
00:02:02,890 --> 00:02:05,280
was executed by people of Ashile Tribe.

33
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:14,600
[Weaving Workshop of Western Suburb]

34
00:02:19,339 --> 00:02:20,538
Wake up!

35
00:02:20,539 --> 00:02:22,299
It's so late now. And you're still sleeping!

36
00:02:25,379 --> 00:02:26,940
Get up now!

37
00:02:32,899 --> 00:02:34,099
Don't you know how late it is?

38
00:02:40,979 --> 00:02:42,140
Look at you...

39
00:02:50,539 --> 00:02:51,249
Miss.

40
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:53,818
After finishing breakfast, leave here immediately.

41
00:02:53,819 --> 00:02:56,618
About your case, I can't afford the responsibility.

42
00:02:56,619 --> 00:02:58,258
Ms. Chai.

43
00:02:58,259 --> 00:03:00,780
I... I... dare not go out.

44
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:04,618
How about... how about letting me stay here?

45
00:03:04,619 --> 00:03:06,299
I can do any work.

46
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,738
You said that you'd leave in one day.

47
00:03:07,739 --> 00:03:09,939
Why are you just hanging on here now?

48
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:11,169
No way.

49
00:03:11,170 --> 00:03:13,139
Leave here after finishing your meal.

50
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,139
Ms. Chai.

51
00:03:14,140 --> 00:03:15,859
I will return to Changan.

52
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:18,220
In several days, I'll definitely leave here.

53
00:03:19,379 --> 00:03:21,579
I can do any work. I mean it.

54
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:22,819
Have you done any work before?

55
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,860
But I know embroidery.

56
00:03:29,619 --> 00:03:30,969
Embroidery?

57
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:32,679
Like the pouch you embroidered?

58
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,978
That's the ugliest pouch I've ever seen.

59
00:03:34,979 --> 00:03:36,699
With such level of embroidery,

60
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:39,579
my weaving workshop has to close someday.

61
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,258
No. Not like that.

62
00:03:40,259 --> 00:03:40,978
Ms. Chai.

63
00:03:40,979 --> 00:03:45,939
That pouch... That pouch was embroidered by my best friend.

64
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:47,379
I really know how to embroider.

65
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:50,898
You look delicate.

66
00:03:50,899 --> 00:03:52,780
I don't think you did any heavy work before.

67
00:03:54,539 --> 00:03:56,419
I have to warn you.

68
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:58,700
Though you can stay here,

69
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:01,739
you won't be paid much.

70
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:07,420
Enjoy your meal.

71
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:30,058
[Virtue Brings Fortune]

72
00:04:30,059 --> 00:04:31,498
Please pause for a second.

73
00:04:31,499 --> 00:04:32,900
I have something to announce.

74
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:40,058
Let me introduce.

75
00:04:40,059 --> 00:04:41,900
This miss is...

76
00:04:44,979 --> 00:04:46,098
Li Leyan.

77
00:04:46,099 --> 00:04:49,219
From now on, she'll work with you.

78
00:04:49,220 --> 00:04:51,818
Yesterday, didn't you say that she'd stay for only one day?

79
00:04:51,819 --> 00:04:53,739
I'm in a good mood today.

80
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:54,978
Can't I keep her?

81
00:04:54,979 --> 00:04:56,098
Surely you can.

82
00:04:56,099 --> 00:04:58,299
But she can't know how to work, according to her appearance.

83
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,859
You can employ anyone but her.

84
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:03,419
I want to employ her, because her salary is low.

85
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,539
I'd love to.

86
00:05:09,499 --> 00:05:10,258
Well.

87
00:05:10,259 --> 00:05:12,739
She hasn't done any work before.

88
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:14,659
Please help her a little bit.

89
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,378
OK. That's it.

90
00:05:19,379 --> 00:05:20,818
Come.

91
00:05:20,819 --> 00:05:21,899
Let's go. Continue working.

92
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,139
Ms. Wei.

93
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:25,498
From now on, she's your apprentice.

94
00:05:25,499 --> 00:05:27,579
This miss will learn from you.

95
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:28,619
Please teach her by heart.

96
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,818
Learn it by heart.

97
00:05:29,819 --> 00:05:31,300
OK. I'll teach her.

98
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,708
This is shuttle.

99
00:05:34,709 --> 00:05:35,708
And this is thread.

100
00:05:35,709 --> 00:05:36,910
Put your feet here.

101
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:39,949
Go through it. Like this.

102
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,108
Then you step on it.

103
00:05:41,109 --> 00:05:42,109
Understand?

104
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:59,708
Tegin, the list of spoils in Shuozhou has been sorted.

105
00:05:59,709 --> 00:06:02,028
Should I send it to Khan's Tent?

106
00:06:02,029 --> 00:06:03,909
Let several reliable men send it.

107
00:06:03,910 --> 00:06:04,910
Yes.

108
00:06:09,869 --> 00:06:11,509
You're not gonna send it on your own?

109
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,629
It's such an achievement.

110
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:15,509
And you don't show your loyalty in front of Great Khan.

111
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:18,669
Since he's very suspicious, he might think you wanna betray him.

112
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,308
I used to let others send it.

113
00:06:20,309 --> 00:06:22,709
If I go there myself this time, he will get suspicious.

114
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,669
What are you doing here?

115
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:29,910
I have something to tell you.

116
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,069
You've seen it.

117
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,509
Sun doesn't want to talk to you.

118
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:36,310
- Just go.
- I can be your military counselor.

119
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,389
Now you're bragging.

120
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:42,028
I mean. Who are you?

121
00:06:42,029 --> 00:06:43,789
Are you making decisions in Eagle Division?

122
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:45,790
Stop driving a wedge between Sun and me.

123
00:06:49,309 --> 00:06:50,309
You...

124
00:06:51,429 --> 00:06:53,268
Your reason?

125
00:06:53,269 --> 00:06:55,909
Since I work for you, and mainly assistant you,

126
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:57,470
I have to do something useful.

127
00:06:58,470 --> 00:07:00,588
I'm good at strategies.

128
00:07:00,589 --> 00:07:03,190
That Tegin brought me here must be out of that reason.

129
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:07,510
Please allow me to be your assistant.

130
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,669
My defeated opponent.

131
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:12,389
You can really brag.

132
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:17,428
Tell me, why should I use a stranger like you as my assistant.

133
00:07:17,429 --> 00:07:20,190
Actually, I've been thinking about a question.

134
00:07:21,269 --> 00:07:24,428
Great Khan let Eagle Division be the pioneer to attack Shuozhou.

135
00:07:24,429 --> 00:07:28,189
However, the army that Tegin led was not for attacking a city.

136
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:31,629
Besides, you haven't fought against Tang before.

137
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:35,868
Therefore, Great Khan seemed not to care about the result.

138
00:07:35,869 --> 00:07:38,390
What's worse, he might want you to lose.

139
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,390
Nonsense!

140
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,349
Go on.

141
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:47,548
It reminds me of what was like in Shuozhou that day.

142
00:07:47,549 --> 00:07:50,069
Eagle Division and Bear Division hindered each other.

143
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:52,428
And you were even competing in public.

144
00:07:52,429 --> 00:07:54,988
If Bear Division wasn't supported by someone,

145
00:07:54,989 --> 00:07:57,268
it's hard for him to do that.

146
00:07:57,269 --> 00:08:00,299
After all, you're the adopted son of Great Khan.

147
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,629
What exactly are you trying to say?

148
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:02,988
So I guessed it correctly.

149
00:08:02,989 --> 00:08:04,868
Tegin's position in Ashile Tribe

150
00:08:04,869 --> 00:08:06,750
is way less solid than what others think about.

151
00:08:07,829 --> 00:08:09,909
But you're the adopted son of Great Khan.

152
00:08:09,910 --> 00:08:11,749
And you have an army.

153
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,909
I don't believe you want to do nothing.

154
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,828
I'm loyal to Great Khan.

155
00:08:15,829 --> 00:08:17,859
Great Khan also trusts me.

156
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:20,069
You don't need to incite between us two.

157
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:23,469
About your words, does Great Khan believe it?

158
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:25,350
Do Great Khan's nephews believe that?

159
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,510
How did you know these things?

160
00:08:31,029 --> 00:08:34,550
So, do you think I'm qualified to be your assistant?

161
00:08:40,070 --> 00:08:41,509
What's your requirement?

162
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:45,428
I'll be your military counselor, and can realize three wishes for you.

163
00:08:45,429 --> 00:08:48,589
However, you can't do harm to Tang.

164
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:50,269
And you can't do ruthless things.

165
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:54,589
When I finish the three tasks, please let me leave here.

166
00:08:54,590 --> 00:08:55,949
Okay.

167
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:57,189
Sun!

168
00:08:57,190 --> 00:09:00,668
From now on, you're no longer a slave.

169
00:09:00,669 --> 00:09:02,589
But I won't help you, either.

170
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:06,589
You need to depend on your ability to survive here in Eagle Division.

171
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:11,189
When you finished three wishes, I would set you free.

172
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:12,190
After that,

173
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,870
if you still want to take revenge on me,

174
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,270
I'd wait for you.

175
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:20,589
Have you decided your three wishes?

176
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:22,069
Not yet.

177
00:09:22,070 --> 00:09:24,308
But it's like making wishes.

178
00:09:24,309 --> 00:09:28,988
The time when I decide it, you should realize it for me.

179
00:09:28,989 --> 00:09:31,589
Okay. I accept that.

180
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:34,868
But just as what I said, you can't do harm to Tang.

181
00:09:34,869 --> 00:09:36,830
And you can't do ruthless things.

182
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:40,389
These days, I'll depend on my own ability

183
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,468
to get a firm foothold here in Eagle Division.

184
00:09:42,469 --> 00:09:44,428
Please wait for my performance, Tegin.

185
00:09:44,429 --> 00:09:45,429
OK. Deal.

186
00:09:47,429 --> 00:09:48,630
Unlock her iron chain.

187
00:09:54,290 --> 00:09:56,610
[Weaving Workshop of Western Suburb]

188
00:10:08,229 --> 00:10:10,589
Let's pause and have a rest.

189
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:11,509
You must feel tired.

190
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,629
I bought some pastries.

191
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:13,788
Everyone can eat.

192
00:10:13,789 --> 00:10:14,629
Pastries?

193
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:15,709
- Pastries!
- Pastries.

194
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:16,868
Come here.

195
00:10:16,869 --> 00:10:17,468
Come.

196
00:10:17,469 --> 00:10:17,868
Thank you.

197
00:10:17,869 --> 00:10:18,908
You all can enjoy it.

198
00:10:18,909 --> 00:10:19,949
- Thanks.
- Thank you.

199
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:20,908
- Thank you.
- Ms. Chai.

200
00:10:20,909 --> 00:10:22,468
Why are you so generous today?

201
00:10:22,469 --> 00:10:23,468
- Right.
- Yeah.

202
00:10:23,469 --> 00:10:25,228
You didn't even buy sesame cakes in normal days.

203
00:10:25,229 --> 00:10:26,189
Did you get any order?

204
00:10:26,190 --> 00:10:27,788
Right.

205
00:10:27,789 --> 00:10:30,949
A businessman Mr. Hu ordered a batch of goods.

206
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:33,428
It's enough for us to spend for several months!

207
00:10:33,429 --> 00:10:34,509
Really?

208
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:36,389
- Great!
- That's great.

209
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,868
So you have to work hard.

210
00:10:37,869 --> 00:10:39,788
After finishing the pastries, continue working.

211
00:10:39,789 --> 00:10:40,908
Okay. Let's go.

212
00:10:40,909 --> 00:10:42,428
Continue working.

213
00:10:42,429 --> 00:10:43,429
That's tasty.

214
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,709
Miss Li.

215
00:10:47,710 --> 00:10:49,269
Have some pastries also.

216
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,668
You can do it later.

217
00:10:50,669 --> 00:10:52,069
You're new here.

218
00:10:52,070 --> 00:10:54,069
I don't have any expectation for you.

219
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:57,149
Whether you do it well or badly, it doesn't matter.

220
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,389
Ms. Chai.

221
00:10:58,390 --> 00:11:01,509
If I do it badly, I can start over.

222
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,428
It doesn't matter.

223
00:11:02,429 --> 00:11:03,468
Eat some pastries first.

224
00:11:03,469 --> 00:11:04,469
You can do it later.

225
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,348
Li Leyan!

226
00:11:10,349 --> 00:11:12,108
What have you done?

227
00:11:12,109 --> 00:11:12,829
Look!

228
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:13,509
Look at it!

229
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,069
Did you see?

230
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:14,908
I'll do it again.

231
00:11:14,909 --> 00:11:15,589
I'll start over.

232
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:17,108
No. No. Don't do it.

233
00:11:17,109 --> 00:11:19,189
Please stop. Please.

234
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:20,869
Look at the thread on your head.

235
00:11:21,989 --> 00:11:22,509
I...

236
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:23,510
That's...

237
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:25,590
I...

238
00:11:27,229 --> 00:11:28,149
Sun.

239
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,908
Great Khan is suddenly coming. And he's with Sher.

240
00:11:30,909 --> 00:11:33,269
Great Khan never came here on his own initiative.

241
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:35,548
I suppose something big might happen.

242
00:11:35,549 --> 00:11:37,428
Could it be about Shuozhou?

243
00:11:37,429 --> 00:11:38,429
About Shuozhou,

244
00:11:39,469 --> 00:11:42,589
it's me that made agreements secretly with Gongsun Heng.

245
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:44,459
You knew nothing.

246
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:47,069
It also has nothing to do with men in Eagle Division.

247
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:48,108
Understand?

248
00:11:48,109 --> 00:11:49,899
What are you gonna do?

249
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,709
Since I accepted Gongsun Heng's offer,

250
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,670
I'd thought about things that would happen today.

251
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:57,269
I made the decision myself.

252
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:58,750
If Great Khan wants to blame us,

253
00:12:00,190 --> 00:12:02,029
you only need to protect yourself.

254
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:05,589
Have you thought of a way to get yourself out of this?

255
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:07,389
No one can be totally sure about anything.

256
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:08,390
I'll do my best.

257
00:12:10,469 --> 00:12:13,229
Prepare the list of spoils to welcome Great Khan.

258
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:22,270
Come.

259
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:26,149
You...

260
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:28,389
Li Shisi. Let me go.

261
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:29,868
Tell me what happened exactly.

262
00:12:29,869 --> 00:12:30,868
I don't know.

263
00:12:30,869 --> 00:12:32,868
Stop playing dumb.

264
00:12:32,869 --> 00:12:34,029
What are you gonna do?

265
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,109
I wanna know the truth.

266
00:12:36,669 --> 00:12:39,389
Pardoning Shuozhou was Sun's own decision.

267
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:41,029
Great Khan didn't know that.

268
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:44,630
If Great Khan were there, almost everyone in Shuozhou would die.

269
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:49,389
Though Sun looks indifferent and cold,

270
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:52,788
he's actually the most humane one.

271
00:12:52,789 --> 00:12:55,348
He already knew it was you that led the army in Shuozhou.

272
00:12:55,349 --> 00:12:58,548
About that arrow to you, he missed the target on purpose.

273
00:12:58,549 --> 00:13:00,509
He even worried if he's too good at shooting.

274
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:03,868
And he kept asking me if you were fine.

275
00:13:03,869 --> 00:13:06,668
Also, before taking you away from Shuozhou,

276
00:13:06,669 --> 00:13:10,829
he posted that you tried to kill the leader of Ashile Tribe but failed

277
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:13,428
and have been executed and died for the people.

278
00:13:13,429 --> 00:13:15,908
That was for your reputation as the Commandant of Shuozhou.

279
00:13:15,909 --> 00:13:16,749
And you?

280
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:17,909
How did you treat him?

281
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:22,228
I don't wanna talk too much with you.

282
00:13:22,229 --> 00:13:24,108
Great Khan comes here this time.

283
00:13:24,109 --> 00:13:26,189
Sun did disobey Great Khan's order.

284
00:13:26,190 --> 00:13:27,829
As for Sher.

285
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:29,749
He's Sun's sworn enemy.

286
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:32,630
If his plot works, Sun will be in danger.

287
00:13:34,070 --> 00:13:35,550
I have to think of a way to save him.

288
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,509
Did Ashile Sun tell you how he would deal with that?

289
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,510
I don't know.

290
00:13:53,429 --> 00:13:55,789
Greetings to Great Khan from Ashile Sun.

291
00:13:56,830 --> 00:13:57,830
Stand up.

292
00:14:16,309 --> 00:14:18,029
Father comes here on your own this time.

293
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:19,390
I wonder what your instruction is.

294
00:14:20,789 --> 00:14:21,950
No need to be so serious.

295
00:14:23,429 --> 00:14:24,468
Take a seat.

296
00:14:24,469 --> 00:14:25,469
Yes.

297
00:14:30,869 --> 00:14:32,228
Sun.

298
00:14:32,229 --> 00:14:34,830
We two haven't seen each other for long.

299
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:38,589
I want to visit here out of whim.

300
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:40,868
Now Eagle Division is well trained and equipped.

301
00:14:40,869 --> 00:14:43,108
Your people all look energetic.

302
00:14:43,109 --> 00:14:44,509
That's good.

303
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,269
I feel relieved.

304
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:49,868
The prosperity in Ashile Tribe owes to father.

305
00:14:49,869 --> 00:14:53,109
What Eagle Division depends on is also father's grace.

306
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:58,389
Sun, that's too modest for you to say that.

307
00:14:58,390 --> 00:15:00,348
I dare not lie to you, father.

308
00:15:00,349 --> 00:15:06,189
I've been hearing that Sun's the God of War here.

309
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:08,829
I thought that was boasting.

310
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:13,099
I didn't expect at the first battle between Eagle Division and Tang,

311
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:17,629
you successfully conquered Shuozhou within only ten days.

312
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:22,789
Sun, you're indeed the God of War.

313
00:15:24,349 --> 00:15:26,749
Ashile Tribe is well known for its battle-wise soildiers.

314
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:30,190
It's natural that Eagle Division can conquer Shuozhou successfully.

315
00:15:31,669 --> 00:15:33,029
Ashile Sun.

316
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:35,629
You're indeed good at the art of language.

317
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:37,710
But you seemed not to have told the truth.

318
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,949
What do you mean?

319
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:43,969
Shuozhou has been hard to conquer.

320
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:45,468
Uncle Khan has been attacking for years,

321
00:15:45,469 --> 00:15:47,589
but still couldn't conquer it.

322
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:50,908
Why did they open the city gate for you once you were there?

323
00:15:50,909 --> 00:15:53,630
Uncle Khan. Don't you think that's too strange?

324
00:15:55,309 --> 00:15:59,429
Sher, tell me why it's strange.

325
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:03,069
Just be straightforward.

326
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:06,009
Great Khan has ordered that after conquering the city,

327
00:16:06,010 --> 00:16:08,509
you have to eliminate all of the soldiers and supplies.

328
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:11,108
Shuozhou is the key place to the northern pass.

329
00:16:11,109 --> 00:16:14,389
Only by so can we give Tang no chance to take a breath.

330
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:17,189
But I heard that after you conquered the city,

331
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:19,548
you not only held an elaborate funeral for Gongsun Heng,

332
00:16:19,549 --> 00:16:21,349
but also pardoned everyone in the city.

333
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:26,228
Ashile Sun, is it because you're afraid of death

334
00:16:26,229 --> 00:16:27,750
so that you want to betray us?

335
00:16:30,549 --> 00:16:33,590
Sun. Is that true?

336
00:16:36,869 --> 00:16:39,789
Right. I did give the order.

337
00:16:41,909 --> 00:16:43,668
Uncle Khan, have you heard that?

338
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:46,989
He admitted that he betrayed you and Ashile Tribe.

339
00:16:49,349 --> 00:16:50,989
Are you doubting my loyalty, father?

340
00:17:01,789 --> 00:17:04,149
He already knew it was you that led the army in Shuozhou.

341
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:06,629
About that arrow to you, he missed the target on purpose.

342
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:08,228
He even worried if he's too good at shooting.

343
00:17:08,229 --> 00:17:10,949
And he kept asking me if you were fine.

344
00:17:12,150 --> 00:17:14,868
As for Sher, he's Sun's sworn enemy.

345
00:17:14,869 --> 00:17:17,829
If his plot works, Sun will be in danger.

346
00:17:19,109 --> 00:17:22,549
Though Ashile Sun didn't do exactly as what Great Khan ordered,

347
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:25,270
he won the battle at such a low price after all.

348
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:29,948
Anyway, that can't be a fault.

349
00:17:29,949 --> 00:17:32,939
Great Khan came here on his own to inquire Sun.

350
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:34,660
There should be something more complicated.

351
00:17:37,109 --> 00:17:38,869
What's that exactly?

352
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:45,509
Go get some water.

353
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,510
Yes.

354
00:17:48,069 --> 00:17:50,068
If it weren't Young Khan that wanna make use of you,

355
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:52,868
I'd definitely beat you to death. Bastard Tang man.

356
00:17:52,869 --> 00:17:55,188
You kept making the request.

357
00:17:55,189 --> 00:17:57,188
Do you really think you're a big figure?

358
00:17:57,189 --> 00:17:59,348
I'll kill you someday.

359
00:17:59,349 --> 00:18:01,149
Tang man?

360
00:18:01,150 --> 00:18:02,949
Why did Young Khan bring a Tang man here?

361
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:20,180
Something's wrong.

362
00:18:21,829 --> 00:18:23,670
If I don't trust you,

363
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:27,549
I won't give you any chance to explain.

364
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,550
Thank you, father.

365
00:18:38,910 --> 00:18:40,749
This is the letter that Gongsun Heng,

366
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,348
governor of Shuozhou, wrote to me.

367
00:18:42,349 --> 00:18:43,469
Please have a check, father.

368
00:18:49,910 --> 00:18:51,868
Gongsun Heng's been guarding the frontier for years.

369
00:18:51,869 --> 00:18:54,188
Our tribe launched many attacks but was defeated by him.

370
00:18:54,189 --> 00:18:56,228
We lost a lot.
[Tegin Sun...]

371
00:18:56,229 --> 00:19:00,229
If I attacked Shuozhou by force, many of our men would die.

372
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:03,348
Gongsun Heng sued for peace this time.

373
00:19:03,349 --> 00:19:05,789
He'd like to suicide for people's lives in that city.

374
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:09,269
When he died, big harm to our tribe would disappear,

375
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:12,790
and we can also win at the lowest price.

376
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:15,070
That's why I accepted his offer.

377
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:18,509
You even pardoned Tang's soldiers.

378
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:19,579
How can you explain that?

379
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:20,789
Most of soldiers in Shuozhou died.

380
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:22,549
There were only old and disabled soldiers left.

381
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:24,068
They can't attack at all.

382
00:19:24,069 --> 00:19:27,709
If not so, Gongsun Heng wouldn't have the request.

383
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:34,669
He killed himself as promised and opened the city gate for us.

384
00:19:34,670 --> 00:19:38,469
As the son of Great Khan, how could I break my promise?

385
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:42,229
Father, please pass judgment.

386
00:19:54,390 --> 00:19:57,389
These are Gong Sunheng's head and the list of all spoils.

387
00:19:57,390 --> 00:19:58,790
Please have a look, Great Khan.

