389
00:20:26,989 --> 00:20:29,670
Enough. No need to check it.

390
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:34,988
Sun. You were right.

391
00:20:34,989 --> 00:20:36,509
The descendants born in the grasslands

392
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:40,389
have always been upright and magnanimous.

393
00:20:40,390 --> 00:20:44,509
Gongsun Heng is a respectable opponent.

394
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:48,988
Just hold the funeral on behalf of me according to our etiquette.

395
00:20:48,989 --> 00:20:50,510
Yes, father.

396
00:21:00,109 --> 00:21:01,708
Sun.

397
00:21:01,709 --> 00:21:05,310
I have another thing to ask you this time.

398
00:21:18,189 --> 00:21:19,859
Nuer.

399
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:20,549
What are you doing?

400
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:21,789
Though you're not a slave now,

401
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:23,228
you still can't order me to do anything.

402
00:21:23,229 --> 00:21:25,859
Nuer. You have to help me this time.

403
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:27,709
You're indeed not taking yourself as a stranger.

404
00:21:27,710 --> 00:21:29,988
Listen, if you don't help me this time,

405
00:21:29,989 --> 00:21:34,150
your Tegin and the whole Eagle Division would face a disaster.

406
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:41,389
Ashile Sun, if you admit it yourself,

407
00:21:41,390 --> 00:21:43,828
I can still plead for you to Uncle Khan.

408
00:21:43,829 --> 00:21:45,708
I don't know what you're talking about.

409
00:21:45,709 --> 00:21:47,910
So you refuse to admit until you face the reality.

410
00:21:50,550 --> 00:21:54,310
Uncle Khan, Ashile Sun colluded with Tang and harmed our tribe.

411
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:57,629
That's venomously slander!

412
00:21:57,630 --> 00:22:00,029
When I was in Youzhou, I could almost succeed.

413
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:02,859
But Ashile Sun, you colluded the envoy of Tang

414
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:04,269
and let him take the army to assist.

415
00:22:04,270 --> 00:22:07,029
Then Tang won back Youzhou again.

416
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:08,750
And my Wolf Division's effort was in vain.

417
00:22:10,189 --> 00:22:14,029
You betrayed Great Khan and colluded with Tang.

418
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:15,988
Stop pretending to be loyal.

419
00:22:15,989 --> 00:22:19,109
Sun, is that true?

420
00:22:21,430 --> 00:22:24,829
I swear to God of Sirius, that it never happens.

421
00:22:26,790 --> 00:22:30,029
Uncle Khan, there's a general betraying Tang.

422
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:33,269
He escaped on his way being sent to Changan.

423
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:34,909
And he's finally under my control.

424
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:37,869
He used to work for King of Lujiang, called Wang Junkuo.

425
00:22:39,510 --> 00:22:42,948
Young Khan, you ruined things in Youzhou yourself.

426
00:22:42,949 --> 00:22:44,868
And now you want to slander Tegin Sun.

427
00:22:44,869 --> 00:22:45,629
What do you mean?

428
00:22:45,630 --> 00:22:47,189
Mu Jin. Stop.

429
00:22:49,229 --> 00:22:53,389
Ashile Sun, you must be familiar with him.

430
00:22:53,390 --> 00:22:56,310
If you haven't done anything, dare you talk with him in person?

431
00:22:58,589 --> 00:22:59,749
Uncle Khan,

432
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:02,709
my men of Wolf Division all died for nothing. That's unfair.

433
00:23:06,109 --> 00:23:07,109
Guards.

434
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:10,510
- Bring the traitor here.
- Yes.

435
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:21,868
I might be insane that I'd follow you here.

436
00:23:21,869 --> 00:23:23,789
You want to do it in front of Great Khan.

437
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:24,828
That's impossible.

438
00:23:24,829 --> 00:23:26,669
Even Tegin Sun can't protect you.

439
00:23:26,670 --> 00:23:28,149
I didn't say I'd do anything.

440
00:23:28,150 --> 00:23:30,389
You won't do anything? You wanna win by just talking?

441
00:23:30,390 --> 00:23:31,750
I indeed plan to win by talking.

442
00:23:32,910 --> 00:23:35,029
Later I'll yell that Young Khan's horse is lost.

443
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:36,149
I'll keep away the guards.

444
00:23:36,150 --> 00:23:37,789
You should finish the rest part.

445
00:23:37,790 --> 00:23:39,429
What do you mean?

446
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:40,708
I'm just here helping you.

447
00:23:40,709 --> 00:23:43,909
The man that Young Khan brought here was the General of Youzhou.

448
00:23:43,910 --> 00:23:44,749
He met me before.

449
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:45,868
I can't go inside.

450
00:23:45,869 --> 00:23:47,309
Only you can do this.

451
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,549
You...

452
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,029
Do you mean it?

453
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:51,108
I'll teach you how to do it.

454
00:23:51,109 --> 00:23:52,868
Come here.

455
00:23:52,869 --> 00:23:54,030
When you get in...

456
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:57,629
Will it work?

457
00:23:57,630 --> 00:23:58,630
It's on you now.

458
00:24:07,989 --> 00:24:09,429
Young Khan's horse's running away!

459
00:24:09,430 --> 00:24:11,110
Young Khan's horse's running away! Get it!

460
00:24:19,229 --> 00:24:21,829
Ashile Sun, have you well considered it?

461
00:24:23,109 --> 00:24:26,909
If you admit your mistake now, maybe Uncle Khan would spare your life

462
00:24:26,910 --> 00:24:28,429
considering your previous achievements.

463
00:24:28,430 --> 00:24:31,669
When Wang Junkuo gets here and explains everything,

464
00:24:31,670 --> 00:24:33,829
you won't feel easy by that time.

465
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:38,068
Even if you don't care about yourself,

466
00:24:38,069 --> 00:24:39,910
you should think about Eagle Division.

467
00:24:42,229 --> 00:24:49,629
Sun, as long as you can admit your mistake and explain yourself,

468
00:24:49,630 --> 00:24:51,189
I'll forgive you.

469
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:55,670
I feel no shame.

470
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:59,150
I haven't done anything harmful to father.

471
00:25:00,150 --> 00:25:02,150
Great Khan. The man is here.

472
00:25:06,310 --> 00:25:07,349
Bring him in.

473
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:25,069
Greetings to Great Khan from Wang Junkuo.

474
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:28,989
Explain to me what happened in Youzhou.

475
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,988
Wang Junkuo.

476
00:25:34,989 --> 00:25:36,989
Have you seen Ashile Sun in Youzhou?

477
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:46,469
Great Khan.

478
00:25:47,589 --> 00:25:50,188
I don't have those things.

479
00:25:50,189 --> 00:25:52,348
I gave the key to Young Khan.

480
00:25:52,349 --> 00:25:56,579
Everything was done by Young Khan himself.

481
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:58,948
As for the loss of treasury, I think...

482
00:25:58,949 --> 00:26:01,588
only Young Khan knows what happened.

483
00:26:01,589 --> 00:26:03,429
Wang Junkuo.

484
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:05,149
What are you talking about?

485
00:26:05,150 --> 00:26:10,429
Explain first what you have seen about Ashile Sun in Youzhou.

486
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:11,988
Please. Great Khan. It's true.

487
00:26:11,989 --> 00:26:13,988
I want to work for you sincerely.

488
00:26:13,989 --> 00:26:16,429
How would I dare occupy the treasury myself?

489
00:26:16,430 --> 00:26:19,348
About those things... Young Khan must have them.

490
00:26:19,349 --> 00:26:20,948
He has been following Tegin Sun.

491
00:26:20,949 --> 00:26:22,630
I think he must want something from Sun.

492
00:26:34,829 --> 00:26:35,389
Uncle Khan.

493
00:26:35,390 --> 00:26:40,188
Ashile Sun, you conquered Shuozhou within ten days.

494
00:26:40,189 --> 00:26:41,549
That was a great achievement.

495
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,429
You deserve a big award.

496
00:26:43,430 --> 00:26:46,988
You can take half of the spoils of the war in Shuozhou.

497
00:26:46,989 --> 00:26:47,989
Thank you, father.

498
00:26:49,989 --> 00:26:55,188
Sun, you seem not to have enough people in your tent.

499
00:26:55,189 --> 00:26:59,789
When I'm back, I'll carefully select several bondwomen for you

500
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:01,708
and send them to your tent.

501
00:27:01,709 --> 00:27:03,069
Thanks a lot, father.

502
00:27:07,229 --> 00:27:09,068
Sher.

503
00:27:09,069 --> 00:27:10,029
Uncle Khan.

504
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:13,389
That's quite a 'good job' this time.

505
00:27:13,390 --> 00:27:14,789
Uncle Khan.

506
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,390
Uncle Khan, please allow me to explain.

507
00:27:45,709 --> 00:27:46,869
I was so scared.

508
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:50,030
Well done.

509
00:27:51,829 --> 00:27:54,099
How did you know about the treasury in Youzhou?

510
00:27:54,100 --> 00:27:55,588
When Wang Junkuo heard that Young Khan

511
00:27:55,589 --> 00:27:57,988
would say he secretly occupied the treasury in Youzhou,

512
00:27:57,989 --> 00:27:59,309
he got panic instantly.

513
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:01,429
Then he didn't remember to slander Tegin Sun.

514
00:28:01,430 --> 00:28:03,789
Actually Sher didn't occupy the treasury.

515
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:05,868
But Wang Junkuo knew nothing.

516
00:28:05,869 --> 00:28:09,068
He had nothing, so he cherished his life very much.

517
00:28:09,069 --> 00:28:11,988
He was afraid that Great Khan would think he stole the treasury,

518
00:28:11,989 --> 00:28:13,909
that's why he said Sher did that.

519
00:28:13,910 --> 00:28:17,188
Actually I just wanted to gamble.

520
00:28:17,189 --> 00:28:19,868
I didn't expect that was quite a success.

521
00:28:19,869 --> 00:28:23,979
It must be because Tegin is lucky, so we could win the bet.

522
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:25,749
Thanks to God of Sirius.

523
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,909
Military counselor. You're marvelous.

524
00:28:27,910 --> 00:28:30,868
You saved not only Tegin, but also the whole Eagle Division.

525
00:28:30,869 --> 00:28:32,630
I really admire you.

526
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:36,270
From now on, we're friends.

527
00:28:59,629 --> 00:29:00,749
I knew you're here.

528
00:29:02,470 --> 00:29:05,868
Every time when Great Khan did something to you due to Sher,

529
00:29:05,869 --> 00:29:08,230
you'd stay here and say nothing.

530
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,350
What happened today,

531
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:13,788
wasn't solved by you, right?

532
00:29:13,789 --> 00:29:16,470
What? You don't think I can do that?

533
00:29:19,389 --> 00:29:20,988
Fine.

534
00:29:20,989 --> 00:29:23,469
It was Li Shisi. He solved it.

535
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:26,628
He can think of different ideas and is good at using people's mind.

536
00:29:26,629 --> 00:29:28,429
I don't know where he got the information

537
00:29:28,430 --> 00:29:31,429
that the taboo here is secretly holding spoils.

538
00:29:31,430 --> 00:29:32,749
That's why he could entrap Sher.

539
00:29:34,749 --> 00:29:36,908
Thanks to my wisdom.

540
00:29:36,909 --> 00:29:40,469
I told him everything about what you did in Shuozhou.

541
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:42,908
Otherwise he might not help you.

542
00:29:42,909 --> 00:29:43,909
You...

543
00:29:47,230 --> 00:29:49,509
Wait. What are you going?

544
00:29:50,950 --> 00:29:51,950
Sun.

545
00:29:54,029 --> 00:29:55,029
Roast lamb leg!

546
00:29:58,110 --> 00:30:00,109
You asked Nuer to keep an eye on Li Shisi.

547
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,470
I think it's not gonna work.

548
00:30:03,389 --> 00:30:04,389
What do you mean?

549
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,869
They live in the same tent.

550
00:30:07,870 --> 00:30:09,589
And today they uncovered Sher's plot together.

551
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:12,069
Naturally their relationship would be better.

552
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:13,508
Look at Nuer.

553
00:30:13,509 --> 00:30:15,669
He treats Li Shisi with food and wine.

554
00:30:17,389 --> 00:30:19,189
Good wine.

555
00:30:19,190 --> 00:30:20,268
You can really drink.

556
00:30:20,269 --> 00:30:22,028
Mu Jin.

557
00:30:22,029 --> 00:30:24,148
Arrange a single tent for Li Shisi.

558
00:30:24,149 --> 00:30:24,868
OK.

559
00:30:24,869 --> 00:30:26,189
I'll do it tomorrow.

560
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:27,190
Do it now.

561
00:30:29,710 --> 00:30:31,429
Look at your eyes.

562
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:33,430
I want to arrange it tomorrow.

563
00:30:36,230 --> 00:30:37,429
Never mind.

564
00:30:37,430 --> 00:30:38,790
I don't care about your pettiness.

565
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,229
One more cup.

566
00:30:43,230 --> 00:30:44,230
Cheers.

567
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:50,628
Really tasty.

568
00:30:50,629 --> 00:30:51,748
Not bad, right?

569
00:30:51,749 --> 00:30:53,109
Why are you here?

570
00:30:53,110 --> 00:30:54,908
Newly roasted lamb leg. Wanna taste?

571
00:30:54,909 --> 00:30:56,069
No.

572
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:58,390
Within only one day, you're already bribed by him.

573
00:31:01,509 --> 00:31:02,909
Bribe?

574
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:05,949
Don't talk nonsense.

575
00:31:05,950 --> 00:31:06,868
Well.

576
00:31:06,869 --> 00:31:09,229
So you can't bear seeing me in harmony with your people?

577
00:31:09,230 --> 00:31:12,430
It's not me that can't bear it, but someone else.

578
00:31:14,749 --> 00:31:16,469
Pack up your things and follow me.

579
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:17,908
Where to?

580
00:31:17,909 --> 00:31:22,148
Since you're the military counselor now, how can you live with Nuer?

581
00:31:22,149 --> 00:31:22,868
Come.

582
00:31:22,869 --> 00:31:24,669
I prepared a wide and good tent.

583
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:53,668
You must forget who you are,

584
00:31:53,669 --> 00:31:55,710
getting drunk in such a little county government.

585
00:31:56,789 --> 00:31:58,748
Isn't it humiliating?

586
00:31:58,749 --> 00:32:00,508
I know.

587
00:32:00,509 --> 00:32:01,669
You despise me.

588
00:32:02,669 --> 00:32:06,748
You think I'm just an indecisive exalted man.

589
00:32:06,749 --> 00:32:08,149
Without my father,

590
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:13,989
in your eyes, I might be even less than a magistrate.

591
00:32:15,029 --> 00:32:16,029
Right?

592
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:21,070
I'm asking you. Yes or no?

593
00:32:23,070 --> 00:32:24,070
You're drunk.

594
00:32:26,989 --> 00:32:28,748
Let me tell you one more thing.

595
00:32:28,749 --> 00:32:31,589
Actually Changge despises me as well.

596
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:32,629
Otherwise,

597
00:32:33,869 --> 00:32:38,149
in all these years, can't she understand my feelings for her?

598
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:42,469
You're still thinking about Li Changge.

599
00:32:42,470 --> 00:32:44,589
I thought you're worrying about Noble Princess.

600
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,989
I am worried.

601
00:32:47,430 --> 00:32:49,868
I'm worried. I'm afraid.

602
00:32:49,869 --> 00:32:51,789
I feel guilty for that.

603
00:32:52,869 --> 00:32:53,909
Leyan is lost.

604
00:32:55,149 --> 00:32:56,909
We haven't found her until now.

605
00:32:58,110 --> 00:33:00,109
Changge is dead.

606
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:02,509
I didn't see her before she died.

607
00:33:04,389 --> 00:33:06,430
I even despise myself.

608
00:33:09,230 --> 00:33:11,788
Come. Sit here.

609
00:33:11,789 --> 00:33:12,909
Drink with me.

610
00:33:18,470 --> 00:33:19,470
So you don't wanna drink.

611
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:22,988
You always look so indifferent about everything.

612
00:33:22,989 --> 00:33:24,748
Isn't it boring?

613
00:33:24,749 --> 00:33:25,950
Have you been drunk before?

614
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:28,749
Have you felt heart-broken before?

615
00:33:31,749 --> 00:33:33,709
Hao Du.

616
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:34,909
I feel sorry for you.

617
00:33:36,029 --> 00:33:42,830
You're like a doll, a doll of... your adoptive father.

618
00:33:49,110 --> 00:33:53,908
Wei Shuyu, if you dare talk any rubbish again, you won't be fine.

619
00:33:53,909 --> 00:33:54,909
Hit me.

620
00:33:57,110 --> 00:33:58,749
I wish you can beat me to death.

621
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:06,430
If I can't find Leyan, I feel ashamed to return to Changan,

622
00:34:07,909 --> 00:34:12,190
and even more ashamed to meet my father.

623
00:34:45,610 --> 00:34:48,330
[County Government in Yunzhou]

624
00:34:55,550 --> 00:34:58,228
Mr. Wei. Good morning.

625
00:34:58,229 --> 00:35:00,309
Have you found Noble Princess?

626
00:35:00,310 --> 00:35:05,508
Not yet. But... Commander Hao has left.

627
00:35:05,509 --> 00:35:06,829
What?

628
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:08,428
- He left?
- Right.

629
00:35:08,429 --> 00:35:10,389
He said it's a waste of time to search together.

630
00:35:10,390 --> 00:35:11,428
Better separately.

631
00:35:11,429 --> 00:35:13,028
He left early in the morning.

632
00:35:13,029 --> 00:35:14,748
Where did he go?

633
00:35:14,749 --> 00:35:17,949
About that... I don't know.

634
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,829
Mr. Wei.

635
00:35:21,830 --> 00:35:22,830
Mr. Wei!

636
00:35:24,310 --> 00:35:26,229
Where are you going?

637
00:35:27,709 --> 00:35:29,229
To look for Noble Princess, of course.

638
00:35:31,110 --> 00:35:32,110
That's...

639
00:36:08,310 --> 00:36:10,590
Greetings to your Majesty.

640
00:36:13,949 --> 00:36:15,229
Wei. Get up.

641
00:36:17,070 --> 00:36:19,389
We've known each other for long.

642
00:36:19,390 --> 00:36:20,748
No need for that.

643
00:36:20,749 --> 00:36:23,509
I dare not accept that kindness.

644
00:36:24,989 --> 00:36:28,988
I need your assistance.

645
00:36:28,989 --> 00:36:34,070
Your Majesty, I'll do whatever I can.

646
00:36:35,949 --> 00:36:36,949
Come.

647
00:36:53,749 --> 00:36:58,669
Your Majesty, I've already known what happened in Jingzhou.

648
00:36:58,670 --> 00:37:01,188
Luo Yi has been good friends with Jiancheng.

649
00:37:01,189 --> 00:37:03,028
The Tianjie Army he leads

650
00:37:03,029 --> 00:37:07,150
has indeed contributed a lot to Tang all these years.

651
00:37:09,189 --> 00:37:10,189
I knew that.

652
00:37:11,189 --> 00:37:14,869
Wei, you don't want the royal court

653
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:18,349
to punish these meritorious officials, but now...

654
00:37:18,350 --> 00:37:20,268
Your Majesty misunderstood me.

655
00:37:20,269 --> 00:37:22,988
I'm not a stupid man caring only about personal feelings

656
00:37:22,989 --> 00:37:25,389
but unaware of loyalty.

657
00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:27,709
No. I just think

658
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:30,670
that you wouldn't want to see me

659
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,708
being ruthless to Luo Yi.

660
00:37:33,709 --> 00:37:34,988
Quite the contrary.

661
00:37:34,989 --> 00:37:37,788
After your Majesty was enthroned, everyone has been pardoned.

662
00:37:37,789 --> 00:37:41,708
But Luo Yi ignored your Majesty's kindness and wanted to revolt.

663
00:37:41,709 --> 00:37:46,228
Jingzhou is a key place to defend Ashile Tribe.

664
00:37:46,229 --> 00:37:49,309
If your Majesty doesn't make a quick move

665
00:37:49,310 --> 00:37:53,948
and eliminate Luo Yi and his Tianjie Army,

666
00:37:53,949 --> 00:37:56,708
I'm afraid the turmoil happened in the late Sui Dynasty

667
00:37:56,709 --> 00:37:58,830
would start again.

668
00:38:00,749 --> 00:38:03,149
Besides, I've got some news

669
00:38:03,150 --> 00:38:06,188
that the traitor Wang Junkuo flew to Ashile Tribe.

670
00:38:06,189 --> 00:38:09,789
But he was killed by Ashile people for some reason.

671
00:38:11,189 --> 00:38:14,709
Your Majesty can't hesitate now.

672
00:38:17,469 --> 00:38:18,830
Wang Junkuo.

673
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:21,829
He was asking for an insult.

674
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:23,428
No one would feel sorry for his death.

675
00:38:23,429 --> 00:38:28,110
After talking with you, I feel relieved now.

676
00:38:29,269 --> 00:38:32,629
But... if Tianjie Army got defeated,

677
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:36,268
Ashile Tribe would definitely swoop in.

678
00:38:36,269 --> 00:38:40,468
Could Tang be safe if your Majesty doesn't deal with Jingzhou?

679
00:38:40,469 --> 00:38:45,670
Would Ashile Tribe stop attacking Tang if it's fine with Jingzhou?

680
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:51,389
Your Majesty, whether showing weakness or toughness

681
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:56,670
wouldn't let Ashile give up coveting Tang's territory.

682
00:38:58,949 --> 00:39:00,150
I understand.

683
00:39:01,789 --> 00:39:04,219
I'll ask General Yuchi to meet me now.

684
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:05,629
Please be assured, your Majesty.

685
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:11,749
Whatever it is, we'd stand behind your Majesty.

686
00:39:16,310 --> 00:39:20,188
By the way, Mr. Wei Junior has been looking for Yan for days.

687
00:39:20,189 --> 00:39:22,829
I think he must have suffered a lot.

688
00:39:22,830 --> 00:39:25,589
I'll arrange more people to search for her.

689
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:26,948
Let him come back now.

690
00:39:26,949 --> 00:39:28,988
I have another arrangement for him.

691
00:39:28,989 --> 00:39:32,549
I also haven't heard from him for days.

692
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:37,220
I think he must feel embarrassed for not having found Noble Princess.

693
00:39:39,110 --> 00:39:43,788
You were too strict with Shuyu.

694
00:39:43,789 --> 00:39:46,988
Shuyu focuses only on searching for Yan,

695
00:39:46,989 --> 00:39:50,309
which must be harmful to his health both mentally and physically.

696
00:39:50,310 --> 00:39:53,988
Fang still needs a Supervisory Censor.

697
00:39:53,989 --> 00:39:55,349
I've thought about it.

698
00:39:55,350 --> 00:39:57,349
Shuyu is perfect for that.

699
00:39:57,350 --> 00:39:58,909
Your Majesty. He's not proper to do it.

700
00:39:58,910 --> 00:40:00,829
Shuyu often makes big mistakes.

701
00:40:00,830 --> 00:40:02,870
It's already decided.

702
00:40:05,310 --> 00:40:06,549
Your Majesty.

703
00:40:06,550 --> 00:40:09,670
Thanks to your Majesty on behalf of Shuyu.

704
00:40:23,469 --> 00:40:24,549
Li Leyan.

705
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:26,228
Do you have too much free time?

706
00:40:26,229 --> 00:40:27,229
What are you doing?

707
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:31,028
I'm just doing it for fun.

708
00:40:31,029 --> 00:40:32,629
You even have the time to do that?

709
00:40:32,630 --> 00:40:35,110
Why didn't you put more strength in working?

710
00:40:36,509 --> 00:40:38,468
I'll learn how to do it soon.

711
00:40:38,469 --> 00:40:40,549
Just give me some more time.

712
00:40:40,550 --> 00:40:44,748
When I was in the Palace, I didn't take charge of such things.

713
00:40:44,749 --> 00:40:45,589
Palace?

714
00:40:45,590 --> 00:40:46,589
Really? Palace?

715
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:49,309
She dreams of being a princess again.

716
00:40:49,310 --> 00:40:53,509
Dear 'Princess', in the Palace, are they using gold shuttles to weave?

717
00:40:57,189 --> 00:41:00,309
Miss, did your head get hit?

718
00:41:00,310 --> 00:41:02,228
Or were you seriously ill?

719
00:41:02,229 --> 00:41:03,829
Why do you keep talking nonsense?

720
00:41:03,830 --> 00:41:05,708
Does she need to see a doctor?

721
00:41:05,709 --> 00:41:08,829
We should ask Ms. Chai not to beat her head.

722
00:41:08,830 --> 00:41:09,949
She's already so dumb.

723
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:21,428
I'll hand these bondwomen to you now.

724
00:41:21,429 --> 00:41:23,389
As for the rest part, you should take care of it.

725
00:41:25,910 --> 00:41:27,708
What's going on?

726
00:41:27,709 --> 00:41:29,468
Bondwomen from Khan's Tent.

727
00:41:29,469 --> 00:41:31,150
It's said to be the award for Tegin.

728
00:41:33,989 --> 00:41:36,268
Tegin never keeps bondwoman in his tent.

729
00:41:36,269 --> 00:41:37,269
Take them away.

730
00:41:39,949 --> 00:41:43,708
How Great Khan treats Tegin is like giving sweets after slapping you.

731
00:41:43,709 --> 00:41:45,268
That's a pity.

732
00:41:45,269 --> 00:41:47,268
You can't tell if those are poisonous or not.

733
00:41:47,269 --> 00:41:51,089
Things from Khan have always been difficult to deal with.

734
00:41:51,090 --> 00:41:52,149
Keep an eye on them.

735
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:53,069
Don't let them wander.

736
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:54,070
Okay.

737
00:42:15,830 --> 00:42:16,830
Mother.

738
00:42:18,709 --> 00:42:20,590
Please turn back and look at me.

739
00:42:22,229 --> 00:42:23,229
Mother.

