00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:33,508
Let me go!

742
00:42:33,509 --> 00:42:34,788
Come.

743
00:42:34,789 --> 00:42:35,949
Let go!

744
00:42:37,789 --> 00:42:39,349
Let go of me!

745
00:42:39,350 --> 00:42:40,708
Don't hide from us, beauty.

